						documentation for more options.
					</p>

					<nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
						<ol class="breadcrumb mb-0 py-2">
							<li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">Home</li>
						</ol>
					</nav>

					<nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
						<ol class="breadcrumb mb-0 py-2">
							<li class="breadcrumb-item">
								<a href="#">Home</a>
